## Supported Timeframes

The API supports various timeframes for historical OHLC data. Please note that different symbols may support different intervals.

| Key | Name | Note |
|-----|------|------|
| MON | Monthly | |
| WEEK | Weekly | |
| DAY | Daily | |
| 240M | 4 Hour | |
| 120M | 2 Hour | |
| 60M | 1 Hour | |
| 30M | 30 Minutes | |
| 15M | 15 Minutes | |
| 10M | 10 Minutes | |
| 5M | 5 Minutes | |
| 3M | 3 Minutes | |
| 1M | 1 Minute | |
